00006 // Eigen based implementation of Fast Moving Natural Evolution Strategy
00007 //    for High-Dimensional Problems (CR-FM-NES), see https://arxiv.org/abs/2201.11422 .
00008 //    Derived from https://github.com/nomuramasahir0/crfmnes .
00009 //
00010 // Requires Eigen version >= 3.4 because new slicing capabilities are used, see
00011 // https://eigen.tuxfamily.org/dox-devel/group__TutorialSlicingIndexing.html
00012 // requires https://github.com/bab2min/EigenRand for random number generation.
